	<p><em>&acirc;&#128;&#152;Guards Club Park will not be used as a depot &acirc;&#128;&#147; instead Network Rail&acirc;&#128;&#153;s own lands will be converted for these purposes.  Also, Guards Club Island Bridge will not be used for access and, as we suggested, barges will instead be used for access and to deliver materials.</em></p>

